{"tid":1037947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入) 中国化工廠爆炸 火柱將人噴上半空","createTime":"2019-02-26T10:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T01:54:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b756555b501fdd11c07363dbd89cfc17644a34e","tid":1037947,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"中國江蘇省一家醫藥化學工廠去年發生一起爆炸事故，工廠內的氫化爐因操作不當發生爆炸，操作者遭火柱噴上半空，當場慘死。日前廠房內的監視器畫面曝光，非常驚悚。<br />\n<br />\n根據馬來西亞《詩華日報》報導，事發地點位於該化工廠的加氫車間，當時時任副主任的王男正在進行氫化爐撤催化劑的作業。由於王男未依程序操作，在氫化爐人孔打開的狀態下，本應填充氮氣保護，不過他卻直接打開了真空汞。此舉導致吸入的空氣與反應爐內的乙醇蒸氣混合，同時催化劑雷尼鎳遇空氣自燃，爆炸的威力也奪去王男的性命。一旁的工人嚇得立即通報，不過醫護人員到場時也只能宣佈死訊。<br />\n<br />\n驚悚影片曝光引發了不少批踢踢網友討論，有多人表示爆炸的衝擊波像是動畫《七龍珠》，不過也有網友質疑該影片的真實性，表示爆炸瞬間將人噴飛，不過「周圍的設備都沒受損」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-V87IqYKrw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-V87IqYKrw4&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfVBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=89e2291c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-V87IqYKrw4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2708730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2708730&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfVBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=aac1e46e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2708730&h=0bb65c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2708730</a>"},{"pid":"a72e3fdbe3bace929ed8dcb802399b446d7c0bdc","tid":1037947,"uid":156995,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8860e917862af1690e2096424dc48d721afcda0","tid":1037947,"uid":202354,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"